Actor - Class in <Unnamed>
Actor object tracks an actor and the movies in which they appear.
Actor(String) - Constructor for class Actor
Constructor sets the actor's name and creates a blank ArrayList of type Movie of the movies the actor appears in.
addActor(Actor) - Method in class Movie
Adds an actor to the list of actors who appear in the movie.
addMovie(Movie) - Method in class Actor
Adds a movie to the list of movies in which an actor appears.
